{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 56321,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "幾分増えていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They had somewhat increased."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56322,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔軍の小部隊や野良モンスター、時には野盗……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Small units of the demon army, wild monsters, and sometimes bandits..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56323,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それらを、辛うじて切り抜けてきた証だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It was proof that she had barely managed to get through them."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56324,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「人類圏までは……もう少し、か……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Just a little further to the human territory...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56325,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今日、夜通し歩けばなんとか、っ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If I walk through the night today, somehow...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56326,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "己を叱咤し、セシルは引きずるように足を動かす。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Chiding herself, Cecil dragged her feet forward."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56327,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（大丈夫……私は、大丈夫、だ、っ……）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(I'm okay... I'm okay... )"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56328,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "人類圏に戻り、再び戦う。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She would return to the human territory and fight again."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56329,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔人は手強いが、退くわけにはいかない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The demons were formidable, but she could not retreat."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56330,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "敗北しようと、地にまみれようと……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even if defeated, even if covered in dirt..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56331,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "身体を、汚されようとも。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even if her body was sullied."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56332,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（彼が……っ、戻る、までは…………！）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Until he... returns...!)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56333,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...........?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56334,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ふと、足が止まった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Suddenly, her feet stopped."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56335,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "目の前に、人影があった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In front of her was a human figure."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56336,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "自分のものではない、影が。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A shadow that was not hers."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56337,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ…………あ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah... ah...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56338,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アリオス……ッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Arios...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56339,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "初めは、幻覚かと思った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At first, she thought it was a hallucination."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56340,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "弱さが見せる、気の迷いかと。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She thought it was a delusion caused by her weakness."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56341,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "しかし、そうではない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But it was not."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56342,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "確かに、勇者アリオス・テオマンは、そこにいた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Sure enough, the hero Arios Teoman was there."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56343,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………セシル」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Cecil.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56344,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………あぁ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56345,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "名を呼ぶ声音も、記憶のまま。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "His voice calling her name was just as she remembered."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56346,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "セシルは思わずこぼれた大粒の涙を、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Cecil involuntarily let fall large tears,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56347,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "慌てて拭った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and quickly wiped them away."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56348,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「久し、ぶり……だ、ずいぶんと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's been a long... long time... quite a while...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56349,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一呼吸足らずの間に熱くなっていく顔に羞恥を覚え、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Feeling embarrassed as her face flushed in less than a breath,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56350,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "セシルは視線を足下に落とした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Cecil lowered her gaze to her feet."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56351,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "胸にこみ上げてくるものが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What welled up in her chest"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56352,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "舌から言葉を奪っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "robbing her tongue of words."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56353,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "再会した時はなんと言ってやろうかと……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She had thought over and over about what to say when they met again..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56354,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何度も考えたのに、何も出てこない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But no matter how much she thought, nothing came out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56355,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あの時……あの時、君が言ったように……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"At that time... just as you said then...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56356,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　君が来るまで、守ったぞ。自由都市を……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I protected it until you came. The Free City...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56357,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "結局、絞り出せたのは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In the end, the words she could squeeze out were..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56358,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "セシルをずうっと支えていた、遠い日の約束だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A promise from long ago that had supported Cecil all along."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56359,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あまり……胸を張れる戦況ではないが。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's not exactly a battle to be proud of,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56360,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　大丈夫だ、君が来てくれたなら、今回も……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But it's okay, if you came, this time too...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56361,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ…………っ、会い、たかった……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah... I wanted to see you..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56362,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ずっと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "All this time...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56363,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"................\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56364,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "縋りつきたくなるような真情と、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Words filled with a desperate sincere emotion,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56365,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "恥じらう気持ちが絡み合った言葉を、吐き出して。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "mixed with feelings of embarrassment, poured out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56366,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...........?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56367,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そこで、ようやく…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then, finally..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56368,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "セシルは、その場の冷えた気配に気がついた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Cecil noticed the cold atmosphere in the place."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56369,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アリオス…………？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Arios...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56370,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "勇者は、じっと、セシルを見据えたまま……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The hero stared fixedly at Cecil and..."
    }
  ]
}

